{"parse":{"title":"Zul'Aman","pageid":305951,"wikitext":{"*":"{{Stub/Location}}\n{{lookingfor|the old 10-main [[raid]] [[instance]] version, see [[Zul'Aman (original)]]|lore about the troll city, see [[Zul'Aman (lore)]]}}\n{{infobox instance\n|name=Zul'Aman\n|aka=ZA\n|ss=Zul'Aman.png\n|caption=loading screen\n|loc=Southeastern [[Ghostlands]]\n|race={{Race|Troll}}<br /> {{Race|Blood elf}}\n|boss={{mob|Daakara|boss=}}\n|type=Dungeon\n|level=85\n|minlevel=85\n|minilvl=346\n|players=5\n|bosses={{Zul'Aman}}\n}}\nThe [[Amani]] [[troll]] city of '''Zul'Aman''' was re-introduced in [[Patch 4.1]] as 5-man [[heroic]] [[instance]].\n\nThough the Ghostlands region is technically a Horde territory ([[blood elf]], to be more specific), the area around Zul'Aman is considered [[contested]].\n\n== Bosses ==\n:''Full boss strategies do not belong in this section or its subsections. Only key abilities or adds should be listed.''\n=== {{mob|boss=|Akil'zon}} ===\n=== {{mob|boss=|Nalorakk}} ===\n=== {{mob|boss=|Jan'alai}} ===\n=== {{mob|boss=|Halazzi}} ===\n=== {{mob|boss=|Hex Lord Malacrass}} ===\n=== {{mob|boss=|Daakara}} ===\n\n== Gallery ==\n<gallery captionalign=\"left\">\nFile:WorldMap-ZulAman.jpg\nDaakara.png|Old Daakara\nDaakara 2.png|Daakara\n</gallery>\n\n== Videos ==\n[[File:How to find the entrance to Zul 'aman - World of Warcraft|thumb|left|335 px]]\n[[File:How to Solo Zul'Aman & Zul'Gurub HC MoP|thumb|right|335 px]]\n{{Clr}}\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Patch 4.1]]\n* [[Zul'Gurub]]\n\n== External links ==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-zone|3805}}\n;Info\n{{elink|type=wowinsider|link=http://wow.joystiq.com/2011/08/22/does-the-rise-of-the-zandalari-dungeon-tier-serve-a-purpose/|desc=Does the Rise of the Zandalari dungeon tier serve a purpose?|bydate=by {{wowinsider|Matthew Rossi}} Aug 22nd 2011 at 1:00PM}}\n;Guides\n{{elink|icon=icyveinscom|site=Icy Veins|link=http://www.icy-veins.com/zul-aman-heroic-dungeon|desc=Zul'Aman Guide (Cataclysm, patch 4.1)}}\n{{elink|icon=wowheadnews|site=Wowhead News|link=http://www.wowheadnews.com/blog=187922/in-depth-boss-strategies-for-zulaman-and-zulgurub|desc=In-depth Boss Strategies for Zul'Aman and Zul'Gurub|bydate=by [http://www.wowheadnews.com/blog&user=Ashelia Ashelia] 4/27/2011 9:18 AM}}\n{{elink|type=wowinsider|link=http://wow.joystiq.com/2011/04/26/patch-4-1-guide-to-the-new-zulaman/|desc=Patch 4.1: Guide to the new Zul'Aman|bydate=by {{wowinsider|Allison Robert}} Apr 26th 2011 at 7:00PM}}\n\n;Old forum discussion\n{{elink|type=bnetwowus|site=Official General Discussion forum (US)|link=http://us.battle.net/wow/en/forum/topic/2140270264#6|desc=Stop complaining about ZA and ZG|bydate=#6 [[Zarhym]] 3/1/11 9:34 PM}}\n{{elink|type=bnetwowus|site=Official General Discussion forum (US)|link=http://us.battle.net/wow/en/forum/topic/2228413625#8|desc=How much do you want to bet that ZG and ZA|bydate=#8 by [[Zarhym]] 3/12/11 3:13 AM}}\n\n[[ru:\u0417\u0443\u043b'\u0410\u043c\u0430\u043d]]\n[[Category:Cities]]\n[[Category:Ghostlands subzones]]\n[[Category:Instances]]\n[[Category:Troll nations]]\n[[Category:Troll territories]]\n[[Category:Zul'Aman| ]]"}}}